Prager 20131022 3 Ultimate Issues: Going Horizontal

Prager H3: There are two types of relationships .. horizontal and vertical.
 Horizontal is your relationship between you and your friends, and you and your spouse.
 Almost all other relationships are vertical .. parent/child, employer/employee,
 teacher/student, and so on.
 You should seek to be loved in your horizontal relationships,
   but not in vertical ones. 
  A Best of Prager Hour. Originally broadcast on January 29, 2008.
